title: Champions and finalists of UEFA EURO championship 1960 to 2016
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 13 different Countrys on X-axis for 2 groups Winner, and Runner-up. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Country Spain had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 2 groups, and it was for Winner. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Country Yugoslavia for Winner.

Country Spain and Yugoslavia had the biggest gap of 2.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for Winner.
